snippet.title: Carnage Trailer
snippet.description:
GleeMill presents the first game play trailer of their upcoming game CARnage. Make your way through the wastelands and survive the Carnage of tomorrow. Wishlist on steam to get notified of demo and release during fall/winter 2024!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2923280/CARnage/
X: https://x.com/GleeMillGames
Tumblr Devlog: https://www.tumblr.com/blog/gleemill-games
